structure.unit: COUNTIES, CITIES, AND OTHER LOCAL UNITS

law.history: Repealed 2014 Ky. Acts ch. 92, sec. 314, effective January 1, 2015. -- Created 1956 (1st Extra. Sess.) Ky. Acts ch. 4, sec. 1, effective March 12, 1956.
